 dipdiydoodagrl@aol.com wrote:
 > Whenever i write anything on the bottom part of the screen and press enter, my computer freezes. There is something that looks like a green recycle sign on the bootom of the screen. What's wrong with it?
 
 Nothing's wrong.  The recycle sign indicates that there's a 
 garbage collection occurring -- unused memory is being 
 reclaimed.
 
 Does your entire computer freeze at that point?  Or just 
 DrScheme?
 
 Are you using a non-English version of Windows?  There are 
 known problems with those.
 
 -- Paul
